{"tid":2505774,"cid":37,"subCid":0,"title":"青協青年宿舍接受入住申請至5月3日 設單人、2或3人共居單位","createTime":"2021-04-27T01:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T02:55:22.000Z","uid":33359,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"82fdb93c9dcdea26f64150a66fe30247a14b70d7","tid":2505774,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T01:02:34.000Z","msg":"青年宿舍計劃提出多時，目的旨在滿足年齡介乎18至29歲、渴望擁有自己居住空間的青年的短期住屋需求。而耗時8年、斥資1.7億元的香港青年協會青年宿舍PH2新一輪入住開始接受申請。既是本港首個青年宿舍項目，亦是不少香港青年在短期住屋方面的熱門選擇。以下為大家整理了單位的情況、申請資格、申請方法，有興趣的青年不妨了解更多。<br />\n<br />\n每個單位均設獨立廁所，租金因應各單位的面積大小及市值租金釐定，已包括管理費、差餉及地租，不包括水電及網絡費用。所有租戶在簽署租約時，均須繳付一筆4000元(單人單位)或8000元(2人單位)的按金，終止租約時，租戶若沒有欠下任何應繳未繳費用，按金將不附利息全數退還。續租租金將參考該年度最新修訂之水平，進行調整。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmZoU8jvVY8m9tEBao7pMWvMnFCpPKCYqCJab1VVqYGSNN?filename=fzZzqg8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfzZzqg8.png&h=61f790e2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b74f741846d9bc314ed950b60c840db8a0613d7a","tid":2505774,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T01:02:57.000Z","msg":"單位師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c8caaadb8c00772e368212cd6d177e8e1a78049","tid":2505774,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T01:03:07.000Z","msg":"青協師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9a5ebb44271716f6236eb959d1b09636774d4f8","tid":2505774,"uid":79793,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T01:03:08.000Z","msg":"自住巴 招sp"},{"pid":"d8b3e567851757d0e70505a98afc1c0e288bf242","tid":2505774,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T01:03:17.000Z","msg":"宿舍師<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b18b2061365b6f4cb84145d47c3d160e534f339f","tid":2505774,"uid":45255,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T01:03:24.000Z","